127
00:10:44,220 --> 00:10:48,300
Jin Joo.

128
00:10:48,300 --> 00:10:51,260
Oh Jin Joo!

129
00:10:53,270 --> 00:10:54,700
Oh Jin Joo!

130
00:10:54,700 --> 00:10:57,940
Na Doo Rim!

131
